# AgToosa Maintainer

Read `docs/agtoosa-maintainer.md` before making changes.

Use this repository mode for generator changes, template changes, platform wiring, version wiring, and bats updates.

**Freeform asks** without `/agtoosa-*` trigger **AgToosa Project Intake** per `docs/AgToosa_Agent.md` → Project Intake Protocol (including **AgToosa Lifecycle Compass**). Always-on detail: `.cursor/rules/agtoosa-maintainer-core.mdc`.

Do not run `agtoosa.sh` install against this repo. For downstream Cursor verification: `bash scripts/cursor-intake-fixture.sh`.
